Member Enumeration Documentation

enum Sonic::ManagedStorage::SDKProperties::SDKProperty_Type

Enumeration of sdk properties which can be retrieved and set.

Enumerator:
LogPath  IN/OUT: Debug logging folder name IN/OUT as String
ConfigPath  IN/OUT: Configuation file name IN/OUT as String
LogFileSize  IN/OUT: UInt64 for debug logging file size in bytes (defaults to 10 MB)
LogLevel  IN/OUT: LogLevelType for debug logging level
Driver  IN/OUT: DriverType for transport filter driver
